parameters: I…I've never seen you around here.
Did you come here from another village?
Uhm…could I be the same kind as you?
"Prince Dahlia, this girl…what is she saying?
The more I look, the more we look similar…
Don't look at the Prince like that!
"Though they call me Prince, this is but a small village.
Just treat me as you would anyone.
(I'm so glad he seems so nice…)
You seem to not be aware you are a Tiny Folk.
I lived with a human Mom.
But, I was abducted by a Tree Frog…
I can't believe you used to live with such a savage race!
She was very kind and warm!
"You must love your human mother, right?
…I apologize for saying such impolite things.
"It's nothing the Prince has to apologize for!
I am sorry…uhm and your name…?
"Miss Maia. I am sorry for the rude things I said
More importantly, there's something I need to ask you.
If it's something I know, I'll do my best to answer.
"I want to go home to Mom.
"I thought if Mom has come here to find me,
then she would come again if I arrive here.
it looks like you aren't on friendly terms with humans.
"It's true that we don't really interact with humans.
I've come into contact with a sole human before.
"But Prince, that merchant only comes once a year…
Once a year, the merchant comes
"Seems like the merchant has a lot of influence,
…I might really be able to go home!
When will this merchant come back?
Please tell me that's not true…!
what if you stayed with us until then?
"A group of 'Tiny Folks Abductors' are coming!!
With that many people, there's not a moment to lose…!
Take the Prince and hurry towards the valley…
So many Tiny Folks…well aren't I lucky!!
Maia! Go off into the back…
